title: ice solvent
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

This flask of jelly-like oil can cover an ice object of human-size or smaller, and takes 10 minutes to apply. After this time, the ice becomes soft and clay-like, and can be formed into any shape that suits your purpose. The ice hardens again after 1 hour.